items.title: Hey 19: Tribe extends streak; 1 shy of AL record
items.summary: One of the more remarkable aspects of the Indians' winning streak has been the level of dominance. That continued on Monday night, and now Cleveland is on the cusp of equaling one of the most famous streaks in baseball history.
